{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idc35b7a17-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s3107"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3107"},"text":"§ 3107.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Individualized vocational rehabilitation plan","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idc35b7a18-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s3107/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The Secretary shall formulate an individualized written plan of vocational rehabilitation for a veteran described in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t38/s3106/b"},"text":"section 3106(b) of this title","children":[],"tail":". Such plan shall be developed with such veteran and shall include, but not be limited to (1) a statement of long-range rehabilitation goals for such veteran and intermediate rehabilitation objectives related to achieving such goals, (2) a statement of the specific services (which shall include counseling in all cases) and assistance to be provided under this chapter, (3) the projected date for the initiation and the anticipated duration of each such service, and (4) objective criteria and an evaluation procedure and schedule for determining whether such objectives and goals are being achieved."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idc35b7a19-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s3107/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idc35b7a1a-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s3107/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The Secretary shall review at least annually the plan formulated under subsection (a) of this section for a veteran and shall afford such veteran the opportunity to participate in each such review.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idc35b7a1b-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s3107/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" On the basis of such review, the Secretary shall—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idc35b7a1c-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s3107/b/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" redevelop such plan with such veteran if the Secretary determines the achievement of the long-range rehabilitation goals for such veteran is—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idc35b7a1d-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s3107/b/2/A/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" no longer feasible due to changes in the employment handicap of the veteran; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idc35b7a1e-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s3107/b/2/A/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" likelier under a different plan formulated under subsection (a); or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idc35b7a1f-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s3107/b/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" disapprove redevelopment of such plan if the Secretary determines such redevelopment is not appropriate.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idc35b7a20-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s3107/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idc35b7a21-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s3107/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Each veteran for whom a plan has been developed or redeveloped under subsection (a) or (b)(1), respectively, of this section or in whose case redevelopment of a plan has been disapproved under subsection (b)(2) of this section, shall be informed of such veteran’s opportunity for a review as provided in paragraph (2) of this subsection.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idc35b7a22-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s3107/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" In any case in which a veteran does not agree to such plan as proposed, to such plan as redeveloped, or to the disapproval of redevelopment of such plan, such veteran may submit to the person described in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t38/s3106/f"},"text":"section 3106(f) of this title","children":[],"tail":" a written statement containing such veteran’s objections and request a review of such plan as proposed or redeveloped, or a review of the disapproval of redevelopment of such plan, as the case may be."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idc35b7a23-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s3107/c/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The Secretary shall review the statement submitted under paragraph (2) of this subsection and the plan as proposed or as redeveloped, and, if applicable, the disapproval of redevelopment of the plan, and render a decision on such review not later than ninety days after the date on which such veteran submits such statement, unless the case is one for which a longer period for review, not to exceed 150 days after such veteran submits such statement, is allowed under regulations prescribed by the Secretary, in which case the Secretary shall render a decision no later than the last day of the period prescribed in such regulations.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idc35b7a24-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/466/tI/s101/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–466, title I, § 101(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-10-17"},"text":"Oct. 17, 1980","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/94/2177"},"text":"94 Stat. 2177","children":[],"tail":", § 1507; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/237/tIV/s423/b/1/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–237, title IV, § 423(b)(1)(A)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1989-12-18"},"text":"Dec. 18, 1989","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/103/2092"},"text":"103 Stat. 2092","children":[],"tail":"; renumbered § 3107 and amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/83/s5/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–83, § 5(a)","children":[],"tail":", (c)(1), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1991-08-06"},"text":"Aug. 6, 1991","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/105/406"},"text":"105 Stat. 406","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/275/tI/s101/f/2/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–275, title I, § 101(f)(2)(A)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-10-09"},"text":"Oct. 9, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/3325"},"text":"110 Stat. 3325","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/119/72/s2"},"text":"Pub. L. 119–72, § 2","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2026-01-20"},"text":"Jan. 20, 2026","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/139/2001"},"text":"139 Stat. 2001","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idc35b7a25-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idc35b7a26-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"idc35b7a27-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Prior section 3107 was renumbered ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t38/s5307"},"text":"section 5307 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idc35b7a28-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2026—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/119/72"},"text":"Pub. L. 119–72","children":[],"tail":" designated existing provisions as par. (1), struck out at end “On the basis of such review, the Secretary shall (1) redevelop such plan with such veteran if the Secretary determines, under regulations which the Secretary shall prescribe, that redevelopment of such plan is appropriate, or (2) disapprove redevelopment of such plan if the Secretary determines, under such regulations, that redevelopment of such plan is not appropriate.”, and added par. (2)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1996—Subsec. (c)(2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/275"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–275","children":[],"tail":" substituted “3106(f)” for “3106(e)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1991—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/83/s5/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–83, § 5(a)","children":[],"tail":", renumbered "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t38/s1507"},"text":"section 1507 of this title","children":[],"tail":" as this section."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsecs. (a), (c)(2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/83/s5/c/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–83, § 5(c)(1)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “3106(b)” for “1506(b)” in subsec. (a) and “3106(e)” for “1506(e)” in subsec. (c)(2)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1989—Subsecs. (a), (b), (c)(3). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/237"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–237","children":[],"tail":" substituted “Secretary” for “Administrator” wherever appearing."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idc35b7a29-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDate","id":"idc35b7a2a-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section effective ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-04-01"},"text":"Apr. 1, 1981","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/466/s802/a/1"},"text":"section 802(a)(1) of Pub. L. 96–466","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t38/s3100"},"text":"section 3100 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"idc35b7a2b-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Individualized Written Plans and Extensions of Eligibility and Vocational Rehabilitation Program Periods for Veterans in Programs on ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-03-31"},"text":"March 31, 1981","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/466/tI/s101/d"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–466, title I, § 101(d)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-10-17"},"text":"Oct. 17, 1980","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/94/2186"},"text":"94 Stat. 2186","children":[],"tail":", provided that with respect to veterans participating in a program of vocational rehabilitation under this chapter on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-03-31"},"text":"Mar. 31, 1981","children":[],"tail":", individualized written plans of vocational rehabilitation were to be formulated under this section as determined by Administrator, and authorized extensions of periods of vocational rehabilitation without regard to certain requirements for determinations of serious employment handicaps."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"idc35b7a2c-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Veterans Pursuing Program of Vocational Rehabilitation Under Former Section 1507 of This Title","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"During the period beginning on ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-10-01"},"text":"Oct. 1, 1980","children":[],"tail":", and ending on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-03-31"},"text":"Mar. 31, 1981","children":[],"tail":", the provisions of section 3112 [formerly 1512] of this title, as added by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/466/tI/s101/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–466, title I, § 101(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-10-17"},"text":"Oct. 17, 1980","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/94/2181"},"text":"94 Stat. 2181","children":[],"tail":", shall apply to veterans pursuing a program of vocational rehabilitation training under this chapter in the same manner as former "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t38/s1507"},"text":"section 1507 of this title","children":[],"tail":" applied to veterans pursuing such a program under this chapter on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-09-30"},"text":"Sept. 30, 1980","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/466/s802/a/4"},"text":"section 802(a)(4) of Pub. L. 96–466","children":[],"tail":", set out as an Effective Date note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t38/s3100"},"text":"section 3100 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
